OL,3,CMan, 91, ordered to stand trial
OL,4,Caccused of causing death of schoolgirl
OL,6,FA 91-year-old man has been ordered to
OL,7,Fstand trial accused of causing the
OL,8,Fdeath of a school girl in Co Antrim
OL,9,Flast year.
OL,11,FEight-year-old Scarlett Rossborough
OL,12,Fwas knocked down and killed while
OL,13,Fwalking with a group of children along
OL,14,FHigh Street in Carrickfergus shortly
OL,15,Fbefore noon on Wednesday, August 9,
OL,16,F2023.
OL,18,FAppearing via video link from his home
OL,19,Ffor a preliminary enquiry into the
OL,20,Fcase was John Noble Lindsay of Prince
OL,21,FAndrew Way, Carrickfergus.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/7
