OL,6,FWatching proceedings from the public
OL,7,Fgallery at Belfast Magistrates' Court
OL,8,Fon Tuesday where family and friends of
OL,9,Fthe late Scarlett Rossborough.
OL,11,FThe 91-year-old defendant is charged
OL,12,Fthat he caused the death of Scarlett
OL,13,FRossborough by driving dangerously on
OL,14,FHigh Street, Carrickfergus.
OL,16,FAsked by the court clerk if he
OL,17,Funderstood the charge he faced, John
OL,18,FNoble Lindsay - dressed in a blue
OL,19,Fjumper - replied: "I do, Your
OL,20,FWorship.''
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/7
