OL,6,F"I am aware that members of the
OL,7,Fdeceased's family are present in
OL,8,Fcourt. We are very eager for this case
OL,9,Fto proceed and I know the family wish
OL,10,Fthe case to move as quickly as
OL,11,Fpossible as well,'' said Mr Molloy.
OL,13,FDistrict Judge Keown said: "I am
OL,14,Fsatisfied there is a case to answer.
OL,15,FThe case will be returned to Belfast
OL,16,FCrown Court for arraignment hearing on
OL,17,Fa date to be fixed.''
