OL,6,FJohn Noble Lindsay was released on his
OL,7,Fown bail of #500 but Judge Keown said
OL,8,Fthe defendant did not have to sign for
OL,9,Fhis bail.
OL,11,FMr Molloy applied for legal aid in the
OL,12,Fcase. He said the defendant had #1,000
OL,13,Fin the bank, #91,000 in an ISA
OL,14,F(Individual Savings Account) and there
OL,15,Fwas #180,000 equity in his home.
OL,17,F"These are serious charges which are
OL,18,Fnow going before the Crown Court which
OL,19,Fis why I am applying for legal aid,''
OL,20,Fsaid the defence lawyer.
