OL,6,FJudge Keown refused the application
OL,7,Ffor legal aid at this stage but said a
OL,8,Ffresh application could be made once
OL,9,Fthe case is before Belfast Crown Court.
OL,11,FScarlett Rossborough was from Larne
OL,12,Fwhere she attended Linn Primary School.
OL,14,FFollowing her tragic death, teachers
OL,15,Fat the school said she was "a much-
OL,16,Floved pupil" who would "always be
OL,17,Fremembered for her infectious giggles
OL,18,Fand sense of fun".
